						<div class="postbody">If you're into gaming, make sure you don't get a laptop with an Intel video chipset.  Their linux drivers suck ass compared to their windows counterparts.  I'm getting like 5-10FPS in WoW under wine w/ minimal settings (except res), but on the same machine I can get it running maxed out w/ 30ishFPS on XP!  I'd put XP, Vista or ReactOS on here, but it's a small 60GB HDD (I really should upgrade it...), &amp; I constantly fill it up w/ anime or Doctor Who, burn it to DVD, then do the same again...</div>

					
